article_title: Basics for signing up for the Affordable Care Act
article_text: Love it or hate it, the Affordable Care Act is inching ever closer to reality. In fact, beginning Oct. 1 — that's next week — Kentuckians will be able to sign up for health insurance through a state-created program at the website, KyNect.Ky.Gov.
